        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>National De-Escalation of Violence and Community Safety Training Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Substance Abuse and Mental Health Services Administration to establish a grant program for de-escalation training in communities.</p>]]></text>
